{"tid":1401314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英懸紅100萬元　緝捕天星碼頭丟國旗落海人士","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:03:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b76e2e6910795a22b1aeb562a2ec24bde998c65f","tid":1401314,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"旺角今日（3日）再有反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行，期間有示威者前往尖沙咀天星碼頭，拆下旗桿上的中國國旗，令國旗在海中漂流。<br />\n<br />\n被指無申報接受澳洲公司UGL五千萬的前特首、現任全國政協副主席梁振英在Facebook宣布，「懸賞港幣壹百萬元」緝捕犯事者。他又倡議成立懸賞基金，協助警方緝捕「借反對修訂《逃犯條例》為名」侮辱國家、衝擊警察、破壞秩序的「狂徒」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3118075/org/4e2c7468c34e2099da54b37aa5336034.png/lSrJ13LSB2EA-4EyyqGVYeOphGkC9dDYg62UkYOtlJE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3118075%2Forg%2F4e2c7468c34e2099da54b37aa5336034.png%2FlSrJ13LSB2EA-4EyyqGVYeOphGkC9dDYg62UkYOtlJE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0e955231&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b2774b21036d29818d166d10223531df46fbf16","tid":1401314,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/359830/旺角遊行-梁振英懸紅100萬元-緝捕天星碼頭丟國旗落海人士\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F359830%2F%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E6%87%B8%E7%B4%85100%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E7%B7%9D%E6%8D%95%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%9F%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E4%B8%9F%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E8%90%BD%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=d56a57d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/359830/旺角遊行-梁振英懸紅100萬元-緝捕天星碼頭丟國旗落海人士</a>"},{"pid":"aab4ec15de35474a2f328652acb34b26fce5a7bc","tid":1401314,"uid":89530,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:37:05.000Z","msg":"5000萬先抽100萬出嚟，點夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji